          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可恨楚邦，暗生诡计，养一个猴头，封为丞相，自负弈棋，无敌于天下，他今\n邀请吾主与哀家前去赴棋盘大会，我想此乃三分请会七分战，只恐到时必有一\n场风波颠险。位此今日登台点将，以防不测。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田常、田玉、田能、管和、田昆、廉赛花",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国母。有用臣等之处，理当尽心尽力，以报我主之恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，听我道来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（叨叨令） 哪怕他重重的罗网奇，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺今番可也难回避。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么意重心诚兄弟谊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告诸臣须记取棋盘会不是待客的筵席。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣驾到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田常、田玉、田能、管和、田昆、廉赛花",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "驾到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，是我背了大王点齐众将，以防不测，不想大王驾到，随我接驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小太监、二大太监引齐王同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见大王！千千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓童，众将为何披挂整齐，聚至教场？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这，妾身要登台点将，调遣人马，预做埋伏，以防万一。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓童差矣。想我齐邦威镇列国，诸侯丧胆，楚邦与我力求和好，此番江楼会棋，\n乃是衣冠之会，如此大兴人马，岂不有碍邦交？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王，想列国争强，各怀心机，外托宴乐之名，内藏甲兵，前车之鉴，大王不\n可不妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，梓童小做安排就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n吩咐击鼓登台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "击鼓登台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "田常、田玉听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田常、田玉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你二人改扮马童模样，随哀家前去赴会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田常、田玉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（田常、田玉同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "田能、管和听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田能、管和",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你等带领人马，埋伏在丹凤岭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田能、管和",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "田昆听令。命你带领三千人马在盘龙山接应，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田昆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊梓童，盘龙山既有埋伏，又何必如此兴师动众，此事倘被列国闻之，不笑我\n齐邦忒胆小了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王，岂不知既防其一，必防其二，有备无患，方为万全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就依梓童，急速启程，荆楚一游。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，还有一事，必须吩咐。\n廉赛花听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此番赴会，命你保护主公，倘会中有诈，急忙保护主公下楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈……想孤身经百战，力敌万人，会中纵然有诈，孤何惧哉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊大王，你可知骄者必败，备者无失？"
        },
        {
          "character": "棋王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就依你。梓童，怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾身身怀有孕了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，廉赛花，你还要备些鲜果，随身携带，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓童，棋盘会上，珍馐甚多，自带鲜果何用啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "著棋之时，我自有妙用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "齐王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看你有何妙用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田能、管和、田昆、廉赛花",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本宫之令。务必小心在意，倘有疏虞，定按军法行事。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上小楼） 正趐起戈戟旌旗，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "违令的难逃刑辟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "护驾前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田昆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，护驾前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田能、管和、廉赛花",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（齐王、二大太监、四小太监、四女兵、大刀手同下。田常、田玉扮马童同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟无盐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马童，带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 动三军举旌旗，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管教那楚国君臣得知俺兵强将勇不可欺。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟无盐、田常、田玉同下。）"
        }
      ],
